'''''The Nightingale's Prayer''''' ni film yo mu misiri yakozwe muri 1959 iyoborwa na Henry Barakat kandi ishingiye kuri novel y'umwanditsi ukomeye Taha Hussein . Irimo Faten Hamama na Ahmed Mazhar .

Mu 1996, mugihe k'imyaka 100 ya Sinema yo muri Egiputa, iyi film yatoranijwe murimwe mu mafilime 150 meza yo muri Egiputa. Yakiriye igihembo cyishimiwe n’ishuri rikuru ry’imashusho y’ubuhanzi n’ubumenyi kandi yatoranijwe  muri Filime nziza y’ururimi rw’amahanga mu bihembo bya 32 bya Academy, ariko ntiyemerwa nk'umukandida. <ref>Margaret Herrick Library, Academy of Motion Picture Arts and Sciences</ref> Yinjiye kandi mu iserukiramuco mpuzamahanga rya 10 rya Berlin . 

